Reincarnation robot

Skill 1- OVERCLOCKED (with Harlequin) Attack speed increases by 1% for every merge rank on the field.gains +0.2% per merge rank once mak is reached
L1 MAX at 30% Attack speed boost 
L2 MAX at 40% Attack speed boost 
L3 MAX at 50% Attack speed boost

Skill 2  -  AERIAL STRIKE (with Phoenix): every 10 parts applied small drones appear, attacking for 5 seconds dealing;
L1:40% of Robot’s Critical Damage in an Area
L2: 50% of Robot’s Critical Damage in an Area
L3:60% of Robot’s Critical Damage in an Area


Skill 3 - MED-BAY PROTOCOL/ CLOUD BACKUP(with Scrapper): A new type of robot is introduced called A.R.A (Advanced Recovery Assistant).
She has a 10% chance of spawning and can't be upgraded with parts.When a robot is destroyed, ARA recovers a certain number of Parts of the destroyed robot.
Recovery triggers when she’s merged with a regular robot and all the parts are transferred. For talent: General program ARA stores merge ranks from destroyed robots.

L1:Cache 7 Parts, 2 merge ranks(for G.P)
L2:Cache 9 Parts, 3 merge ranks(for G.P)
L3 Cache 12 Parts, 4 merge ranks(for G.P)
